{"tid":661502,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"老母同人夾份係大陸開酒樓","createTime":"2018-05-11T15:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T16:02:33.000Z","uid":164094,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c9da2eaab18c6d702f1c7832191aa9acf116a8eb","tid":661502,"uid":164094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"如題，老母（香港人）同一個朋友同2個大陸親友夾份係大陸開左間酒樓，由一位大陸親友打理，即係個位親友係法人，而我屋企人同其餘2個人就係股東，大家各佔1/4。<br />\n<br />\n想問如果間酒樓有任何債務問題，我屋企人除左一開始投資落去既金額之外，仲需唔需要付上額外既責任? 大陸又追唔追到落黎香港?<br />\n<br />\n例如 酒樓既法人用公司名義問銀行借左錢走佬等等"},{"pid":"df3755a334b1d1999783013e997400e219169475","tid":661502,"uid":135767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff29d0a25476bcbc962958f57d0e81e980a9c796","tid":661502,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:50:50.000Z","msg":"冇法治ga wor"},{"pid":"ec676bc516b9276da9d257d65ae75a0d7de15d01","tid":661502,"uid":164094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df3755a334b1d1999783013e997400e219169475","tid":661502,"uid":135767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:55:11.000Z","msg":"人如其名"},{"pid":"c16f649b3fee532cc13b2934fbb5866d73461197","tid":661502,"uid":114270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:59:47.000Z","msg":"我琴晚見到你老母同個男人入左酒樓"},{"pid":"663856d0e629743a1f1389e7ef8f7e43310228b0","tid":661502,"uid":51436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:59:58.000Z","msg":"十個同大陸人夾份做生意十個都奶野，你阿媽真係沙膽"},{"pid":"ed331d3a6ad8efb7871264e2fa0d8fda12aa3560","tid":661502,"uid":164094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c16f649b3fee532cc13b2934fbb5866d73461197","tid":661502,"uid":114270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T15:59:47.000Z","msg":"我琴晚見到你老母同個男人入左酒樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"係啊